ntità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic001192.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface> -->\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"grc\" resp=\"#MH\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>οἱ ἀλειφόμε\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">νοι\u003C/supplied>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>\u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname>Ἀγάθαρχον\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\"/>\u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname type=\"patronym\">Ἡρακλείου\u003C/name>\u003C/persName>\u003C/persName>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\n                        \u003Cnote>Text according to Kaibel in IG\u003C/note>\n                    \u003C/app>                   \n                    \u003Capp loc=\"2\">\n                        \u003Cnote>Gualtherus: ΑΝΑΟΑΡΧΟΝ. Bartholini: ΑΝΑΣΙΑΡΧΟΝ. Wilamowitz: Ἀνά[ξ]αρχον.\u003C/note>\n                    \u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#MH\">\n                \u003Cp>The annointed (honour) Agatharchos, son of Herakleios.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>The stone was seen by Gualtherus, but (contra Fuduli 2017: 176, who seems to misread Salinas' report in NSA 1880, pp. 191-195, referring a description of IG XIV.370 to this text), was no longer discoverable when Salinas visited in 1880. \u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IG\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Kaibel\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1890\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>\n                            \u003Cref target=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\">369\u003C/ref>\n                        \u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/Q2SBPG9F\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Gualtherus\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1624 [1625]\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>316\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/ZP8DE8KS\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Castelli\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1769\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>cl.6 no.2\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/SPTB56H3\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"CIG\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Franz\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1853\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>5609\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"